{"tid":688724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一秒激怒台灣人？ 網友一致認為只要被這樣稱呼...","createTime":"2018-06-03T13:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T01:49:07.000Z","uid":35790,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e30ff43cad9de6f2ba976bb04c97c191c8f9ad5d","tid":688724,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:03:08.000Z","msg":"一秒激怒台灣人？ 網友一致認為只要被這樣稱呼...<br />\n<br />\n2018-06-03 19:35<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕有網友在PTT上發文詢問「如何一秒激怒台灣人？」引起網友熱烈討論。許多人紛紛在底下留言，其中最多人覺得，會被激怒的話，是被別人稱作「中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n該名網友在PTT上發文詢問，依照現在中國、台灣對立的情況，「該如何用一句話瞬間激怒台灣人呢？」瞬間吸引許多網友在底下留言討論。<br />\n有網友表示，「中國人」、「中國台灣」、「大陸」、「內地」都是很敏感的詞彙，也有網友認為，聽到「兩岸一家親」、「大家都是中國人」，或是被中國人嘲諷「灣灣」、「台巴子」都會讓人一秒生氣，不過多數的意見，還是認為被稱為「中國人」是最讓人不開心的。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"7b4d32c67206987ebe4330ee83132b223c74aceb","tid":688724,"uid":59283,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"香港都係"},{"pid":"976eb188d43e754e3e2994c636a3a9afda0968a0","tid":688724,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef565f7eecef37a41fb351343fe047bb7b08049","tid":688724,"uid":35790,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://g.udn.com.tw/upfiles/B_KA/kalaok/PSN_PHOTO/803/f_12298803_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg.udn.com.tw%2Fupfiles%2FB_KA%2Fkalaok%2FPSN_PHOTO%2F803%2Ff_12298803_1.jpg&h=3e14ee2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ab430e4d11766b13bbbb5ef309852ed05f044d3","tid":688724,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"7b4d32c67206987ebe4330ee83132b223c74aceb","tid":688724,"uid":59283,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"香港都係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:30:49.000Z","msg":"邊句一秒辣㷫香港人：<br />\n<br />\nA. 冇民主<br />\nB. 冇得睇TVB<br />\nC. 香港人即系中國人<br />\nD. 𨳒你老母"},{"pid":"35ed5d8fd0e3a55b346d65940746e04ae0c670c4","tid":688724,"uid":25038,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"其實好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人同台灣人互鬧係不停話對方係支那人<br />\n不過唔係講笑，呢句嘢真係難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fadc2fe798372ca374d0cf3ebd0579bdecdff2a","tid":688724,"uid":46245,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cef565f7eecef37a41fb351343fe047bb7b08049","tid":688724,"uid":35790,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://g.udn.com.tw/upfiles/B_KA/kalaok/PSN_PHOTO/803/f_12298803_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg.udn.com.tw%2Fupfiles%2FB_KA%2Fkalaok%2FPSN_PHOTO%2F803%2Ff_12298803_1.jpg&h=3e14ee2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:38:44.000Z","msg":"似乎我係識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49a4074d44c58af68f16f24172a4213f8f732a9","tid":688724,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ed5d8fd0e3a55b346d65940746e04ae0c670c4","tid":688724,"uid":25038,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"其實好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人同台灣人互鬧係不停話對方係支那人<br />\n不過唔係講笑，呢句嘢真係難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:38:51.000Z","msg":"用胡語講仲難聽"},{"pid":"2d140258b850571696cdf910ae81301d43519f8c","tid":688724,"uid":46245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"35ed5d8fd0e3a55b346d65940746e04ae0c670c4","tid":688724,"uid":25038,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"其實好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人同台灣人互鬧係不停話對方係支那人<br />\n不過唔係講笑，呢句嘢真係難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/n